reviewText: My grandkids loved it!!!  I am not too keen on the 'new' Veggie Tales' however this one was done well.
Standard Veggie Tales, cute and thoughtfully made. All the same line up of characters with fun songs and catchy scenes.

I can't say enough good things about the Veggie Tales collection of movies. If you could go back and do things different in your life would things be better? This is the approach of the subject matter to this well thought through Christian movie.

I really loved how this Veggie Tales made the classic "It's a Wonderful Life" for kids, and put a Christian outlook to it, of course. Children should be reminded to be charitable and that every person is important somehow. Great story!
